guru ( marathi : गुरू ) is a 2016 marathi language action film directed by sanjay jadhav and produced by sunil lulla , deepak pandurang rane and bagpiper soda . the film stars ankush choudhary and urmila kanitkar in lead roles . film marks the fourth collaboration of actor-director duo ankush choudhary and sanjay jadhav and first after their blockbuster outing duniyadari . film has a planned release of 22 january 2016 . film is a one of a kind content partnership between united spirits ’ bagpiper soda and eros international . through a unique association , bagpiper soda will be an integrated partner across the film ’s content , promotions and performance . official teaser of the film is released on 18 november 2015 . first official poster of the film designed by sachin gurav was unveiled in an event while official trailer went online on 30 december .